{"tid":2515954,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[錶撚入] 擺低你哋戴緊嘅錶(78)","createTime":"2021-05-04T10:27:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T11:11:07.000Z","uid":138996,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"e20db9074ed4e6d5333a72690a048464f2e203c4","tid":2515954,"uid":138996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T10:27:10.000Z","msg":"各位繼續 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nprevious: (77)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2496839/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2496839/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"fcd871f69e0c70baad79335dd22f75999b9ed191","tid":2515954,"uid":138996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T10:27:30.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">【注意事項】</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">1）避免購買行貨 Seiko / Grand Seiko，全面封殺香港代理「通城」</span><br />\n<br />\n罪證：2019 年勾結黑警散仔協會，推出散仔協會 42 週年特別版手錶<br />\n<br />\n通城作為香港代理，必定跟事件有關，做法完全係同廣大香港精工用家過唔去<br />\nSeiko HQ 作為生產商亦責無旁貸<br />\n真係要買精工，請買水貨，一蚊都唔好俾通城賺 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmd8qoNiwxt81RBQxJHQpFTTiJdcXffwNg7BLG4wraF3YB?filename=OijcG73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOijcG73.jpg&h=fdd2b665&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">2）買錶還買錶，最緊要唔好買 BALL</span><br />\n<br />\n罪證：2015 年勾結黑警散仔協會，推出「警務精英特別版」手錶<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-06-2015/20422\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F01-06-2015%2F20422&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnle0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=92263638\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-06-2015/20422</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPpXw3j3Yk5HurRogTp4usAJgiZHACjFP9Krak84WCtTA?filename=QjchTdT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQjchTdT.jpg&h=0ed1e068&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">3）Casio 都古古惑惑，大家自己留意</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeMRmgMsCmVxQ18eKhErxMGjJAC9Ly2DSngT6RR7GShpg?filename=8zMjJXN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8zMjJXN.png&h=50b5209c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4c433a13a37f1e3c84bc212ce5fc7019be9e2fb","tid":2515954,"uid":138996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T10:27:52.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">【FAQ】</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">1）點解貼親 Rolex 同 Panerai 都收到咁多負皮嘅？</span><br />\n<br />\n呢度係咁，入鄉隨俗啦，大家冇惡意嘅。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">2）你哋平時講嗰啲 RR 同埋 M 係咩嚟？</span><br />\n<br />\n香港其中兩間買水貨錶價錢比較相宜，質素有一定保證嘅舖頭。<br />\nso far 冇聽過有人買到假嘢。<br />\n<br />\n一間係稀有稀有 R__e R__e，另一間係 M_____z。請自己再 search。<br />\n雖然較平，呢類舖貨源相對冇咁穩定，想出手前建議再問下對方確認。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">3）咩叫 BT，咩叫 AD？</span><br />\n<br />\nBT 即係 Boutique，品牌專門店，係錶廠公司自己開，唔係香港代理開。折頭少甚至冇折頭，但款式齊，服務好。<br />\n<br />\nAD 即係 Authorised Dealer，一間錶行拎咗錶廠嘅代理權，可以賣佢啲錶。一間錶行通常唔會只係得一個品牌，一賣就賣十個八個 brand。折頭多啲，但款式冇咁多，服務同埋 sales 對個別品牌認識一定冇 BT 咁好。<br />\n<br />\n各位自己揀。"},{"pid":"edff77049882b67bc0c4187721eeada03a654167","tid":2515954,"uid":47422,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T10:42:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYWdvjJUqMEi7qrXkJQTD4p38Mr8GaBrXwt8QmJi2CQJW?filename=28Mrwaf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F28Mrwaf.jpg&h=03f7f595&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfPs9UHaDDRHqAs3zpEvEeCiEKZCWsT48Zp3e9bfadNgD?filename=3PVzE3B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3PVzE3B.jpg&h=40dfe23e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搶第一"},{"pid":"ceea9b3f2bc0cb226c2adb3ac347ebb5386f0ee0","tid":2515954,"uid":75493,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"edff77049882b67bc0c4187721eeada03a654167","tid":2515954,"uid":47422,"like":7,"dislike":0,"sc